Feline2::

She kissed him and slowly, raised her arms and put them around his 
neck.  She wasn't sure what he ment by 'the right time' but she 
figured she'd find out eventually. She kissed him and felt her spark 
speed up even faster.  Her whole body tingled. 

"Ah, what now? I mean, with you being a maximal and all, won't the 
Allience try to kill you now? Shouldn't we leave? of find some way to 
make you a predacon again so you can stay here?"
